Woji bụ obodo dị na Obio-Akpor Local Government Area na Rivers State, Nigeria.

Obodo Woji gbara elelenwo gburugburu, Artillery, Slaughter, Rumukrushi, wdg.Ụlọ ọrụ, Omahia Mmanụ Ụgbọala, ụka, nnukwu ụlọ ahịa, ụlọ akwụkwọ na ụlọ akụ wdg dị na mpaghara obodo mepere emepe nke Woji, Rivers State.
Obodo woji nwere okporo ámá na ala dị iche iche dị ka Federal Housing Estate Woji wdg.
Obodo Woji nwere osimiri aha ya nke a na-akpọ Osimiri Woji.
